                These Early Access Terms and Conditions (the "Agreement") are entered into between the user ("User" or "you") of the Force Field platform and real-time LLM firewall solution (the "Solution") and 9558-6616 Québec Inc. ("Force Field", "we", or "us"). The "Solution" means the beta version of a platform and AI-powered tool consisting of a security layer that sits between End Users and LLM-powered knowledge systems.
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300 font-semibold uppercase text-sm tracking-wide">
