              Force Field shall own all rights, title and interest in and to any suggestions, requests or recommendations for improvements or enhancements to the Solution or other feedback that User may, alone or jointly with Force Field, propose or make during the Early Access Period (collectively, "Feedback"). User hereby irrevocably (i) assigns all User's rights, title and interest in and to the Feedback to Force Field; and (ii) waives in favour of Force Field any and all moral rights that User has or may have in the Feedback. User further agrees to provide Force Field such assistance as it may require to document, perfect, and maintain its rights to the Feedback.
