              Force Field shall make the Solution available to User during the Early Access Period, solely for the purpose of User's use thereof. Force Field may, at its sole discretion, provide User such technical assistance as it may deem necessary. Force Field may impose certain limitations on the use of the Solution during the Early Access Period. Upon reasonable prior notice to User, Force Field may also delete all data from the Solution, which deletion would include any User Content. In such event, Force Field's reasonable prior notice would permit you to download and save any User Content prior to such deletion.
