              Unless terminated earlier, this Agreement will begin on the Effective Date and will automatically terminate on the date on which a generally available commercial version of the Solution is released and a new Terms and Conditions covers the User's use (such term being defined as the "Early Access Period"). Force Field may terminate this Agreement at any time for any reason. User may terminate this Agreement at any time by notifying Force Field and/or by ceasing all use of the Solution. Any provision which by its nature should survive termination or expiration will survive.
