            <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300">
              User shall not, during the Early Access Period or thereafter, directly or indirectly, (i) criticize, disparage, defame or make or post any negative comments or reports about the Solution or Force Field, whether oral or written, including via social media or the internet; or (ii) take any action that might impair the integrity, reputation or goodwill of Force Field or its Representatives.
